define gui.about = _("Every plate served has a price, and every fortune has a sacrifice.\n\nWelcome to Dapur Tirto, where the delicious aroma of cooking hides the foul stench of ancient rituals. What began as a culinary quest for glory slowly turned into an inescapable curse. Behind every legendary recipe lies a dark secret about the lives sacrificed to reach the pinnacle of success.\n\nDishroom Bloody is a psychological horror visual novel that takes you through the dark corridors of Dapur Tirto. Follow the Trio Investigators as they uncover a conspiracy of sacrifices for eternal wealth. Remember: in this place, the customers aren't the only ones who must be served.")